-- Nirma Surges in Mumbai on Plan to Buyback Shares, Take Company Private
-- B y   A r i j i t   G h o s h
-- 2010-10-11T03:38:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-11/nirma-surges-in-mumbai-on-plan-to-buyback-shares-take-company-private.html
Nirma Ltd. surged in Mumbai trading
after the company said it will pay 235 rupees to buyback shares
and take the company private.  The shares gained 13.9 percent to 254.8 rupees at 9:06 a.m.
in Mumbai.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
